<br>
You ask, you get nothing.<br>
<br>
I spent a couple hours yesterday in Shadowweavers just doing drive by buffing. Some folks may have saw me at the banker, I would sit, chat in guildsay and folks that came in hurt got regen, everyone got sow.<br>
<br>
What frosts my arse is when I log in, or land at a ring, and immediatly get sent DIRECT TELLS asking for ports. <br>
<br>
I mean we are talking (this actually happened to me last week and was the straw that broke this camels back)...<br>
<br>
Selsect Server...<br>
Select Character...<br>
Welcome to West Commondlands..<br>
Sosandso tells you  &quot;Hello&quot; &lt;--- very first message in my chat bar.<br>
You tell Soandso &quot;Hello Sir. Good morning.&quot;<br>
(every Druid here KNOWS what the next line was)<br>
<br>
Long story short, I was late for a Raid in Kith and did not port him to GD, but memmed Misty Thicket and got moving...<br>
<br>
Welcome to Misty Thicket..<br>
SoandSo01 tell you &quot;Good morning&quot;<br>
You tell Soandso01 &quot;Hello Sir. Good morning.&quot;<br>
SosanSo01 tells you &quot;Can you port me to Freerott?&quot;<br>
(GAAAAAHHHH!!!!!!)<br>
<br>
GDI just OOC it, if I am busy, I will not answer, if I am free I WILL respond. Just don't press me with a tell to respond. After almost 40 levels, I finally broke down and went /role because I just got tired of having to explain to people why I did not have the time AT THAT MOMENT to port them. <br>
<br>
I also gave up my +wis 1HB in lieu of a Ice War Claw 1HS with no stats. And, when at all possible I wield a Parrying Dagger in my offhand. Now I look like a Ranger.<br>
<br>
Oh and before anyone starts with the &quot;but you don't know what it's like to be a (insert non-porting class name here)&quot; reply, look at my sig and what my main is. ;) Trust me I do know.<br>
<br>
And you know who ruined my kind hearthedness? Those non-porting class people who send me direct tells before my screen even draws, then when I did have time to port them from WC to DL, before I zone in, they are already half way to the tunell and give me the &quot;K, tnx, l8r bye!&quot; and disband. (welcome to my ignore list bud) <p><body lang=EN-US style='tab-interval:.5in'>

